public class IngestDeleteRequestBuilder
extends org.elasticsearch.action.ActionRequestBuilder<IngestDeleteRequest,IngestResponse,IngestDeleteRequestBuilder>

A bulk request holds ordered DeleteRequests and allows to executes it in a single batch.
